{"tid":1633020,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［急］ 10月7日 勇武抖抖先好無。。。","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:11:48.000Z","uid":229709,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"afc7971d00ef258eead9e3acd97da3ed9b9d2484","tid":1633020,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"律師朋友提醒前線 ：<br />\n<br />\n//其實777知佢仲未可以動用到緊急法，但佢特登令我地自己營造緊急打仗狀態，到司法覆核既時候佢既律師就可以同法庭講 &ldquo;係呀之前都可能未justified 但依家就唔同啦&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n星期五第一個司法覆核就係咁輸<br />\n<br />\n岩岩今日入court 個份係本世紀最強既律師團一齊整，真係寫得好好，但如果我地又自己搞到打仗咁就完全幫緊林太。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個覆核成功，成條緊急法都會被廢除，個盒唔會再有人有得玩。//<br />\n<br />\n今日休息下，俾和理非/大律師做野，我地絕不割蓆不篤灰，今日係做國際文宣，比外媒影相，今日唔裝唔放火。最尾衰左，前線先出手！<br />\n<br />\n高院受理左司法覆核，一定要同律師同一陣線，唔好俾機會政府！<br />\n<br />\nFrom: FB"},{"pid":"3685907c8c2c16796c64bd3f07962a0b06eeee6b","tid":1633020,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:57:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"fb744491f8f4836be064eb6e4935c970e13e1d9d","tid":1633020,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dd2b943a14ffa05f1716dcc6f7d26c8acf279ca","tid":1633020,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:58:51.000Z","msg":"停到人權法過左先"},{"pid":"577f5eb31b2a9e9149188a806a01e808c0e80f52","tid":1633020,"uid":18223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67bec049c3d61854f958eb23756355e94363989d","tid":1633020,"uid":309137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90cc837a2a7b200c4df14f4b67fd1c40071c4b30","tid":1633020,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fy6PwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fy6PwF.png&h=ea9a012e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4uNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=76de5926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a><br />\n<br />\n關於民權法，要講清楚，美國並不要求大家和平<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632886</a><br />\n<br />\n「戰略」搏一個星期，我地可以贏一世<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630040</a>"},{